'''達娜·泰瑞斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Dana Terrace'''}}，{{bd|1990年|12月8日|catIdx=Terrace}}），[[美國|美國]]女性[[動畫師|動畫師]]、[[作家|作家]]、[[導演|導演]]。她是[[迪士尼頻道|迪士尼頻道]]電視動畫《[[奇幻貓頭鷹小屋|奇幻貓頭鷹小屋]]》的創作者，其他參與過的主要作品包括《[[神秘小鎮大冒險|神秘小鎮大冒險]]》及《{{link-en|新唐老鴨俱樂部|DuckTales (2017 TV series)}}》<ref>{{Cite web|last=Murphy|first=Jackson|date=January 6, 2020|title=INTERVIEW: Creator Dana Terrace on Disney's "The Owl House"|url=http://www.animationscoop.com/interview-creator-dana-terrace-on-disneys-the-owl-house/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320142236/http://www.animationscoop.com/interview-creator-dana-terrace-on-disneys-the-owl-house/|archive-date=2020-03-20|access-date=September 3, 2020|website=Animation Scoop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
達娜·泰瑞斯於2015年起與同為動畫師，《[[神秘小鎮大冒險|神秘小鎮大冒險]]》的創作者{{link-en|亞歷克斯·赫希|Alex Hirsch}}交往<ref>{{cite tweet|last=Hirsch|first=Alex|authorlink=Alex Hirsch|user=_alexhirsch|number=677721706174124032|date=December 18, 2015|title=Noticed that my girlfriend @DanaTerrace looks eerily similar to Dana Scully and now I can't un-see it|accessdate=September 4, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412201723/https://twitter.com/_alexhirsch/status/677721706174124032|archivedate=April 12, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref> 。2017年起泰瑞斯公開自己為[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]者<ref>{{cite tweet |last=Terrace |first=Dana |authorlink=Dana Terrace |user=DanaTerrace |number=1292245190095208448 |date=August 8, 2020 |title=Congratulations! I'm so happy you enjoyed the episode and it meant that much to you. It was a giant crew effort. Creating these characters led me to come out as bi to my friends and fam back in 2017, I hope they continue to create positive vibes for ppl in future eps! 🦉 🌈 |accessdate=August 9, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809160950/https://twitter.com/DanaTerrace/status/1292245190095208448 |archivedate=August 9, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lezsmeeting.com/post/read/1500|title=迪士尼頻道首度出現雙性戀主角，《奇幻貓頭鷹小屋》創作者：我得到強大支持|publisher=女人國|access-date=2020-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126235944/https://lezsmeeting.com/post/read/1500|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來並藉鑑她的經歷創造了《奇幻貓頭鷹小屋》的雙性戀主角—14歲女孩露絲·諾西達（Luz Noceda），泰瑞斯多次提到她從自己身上獲取了創作露絲的靈感。由於迪士尼頻道一直被認為在[[LGBT|LGBTQ+]]議題上過於保守，因此《奇幻貓頭鷹小屋》的創作被視為重大的里程碑<ref>{{cite web|url=https://lalatai.com/tvmovie/news/%E5%AF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%87%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%A2%91%EF%BC%81%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E5%BD%B1%E9%9B%86%E3%80%8A%E5%A5%87%E5%B9%BB%E8%B2%93%E9%A0%AD%E9%B7%B9%E5%B0%8F%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%8B-%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%99%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92|title=寫下突破性里程碑！迪士尼動畫影集《奇幻貓頭鷹小屋》-以雙性戀者為主角|publisher=Lalatai|access-date=2020-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129163407/https://lalatai.com/tvmovie/news/%E5%AF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%87%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%A2%91%EF%BC%81%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB%E5%BD%B1%E9%9B%86%E3%80%8A%E5%A5%87%E5%B9%BB%E8%B2%93%E9%A0%AD%E9%B7%B9%E5%B0%8F%E5%B1%8B%E3%80%8B-%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%99%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

